color listnormal        red black
color listnormal_unread red black
color listfocus         red black bold reverse
color listfocus_unread  red black bold reverse
color info              red black reverse bold
color background        red black
color article           red black

browser "open %u"

bind j everywhere down
bind k everywhere up
bind h everywhere quit
bind l everywhere open
bind g everywhere home
bind G everywhere end
bind ^d everywhere pagedown
bind ^u everywhere pageup
bind ^f everywhere pagedown
bind ^b everywhere pageup
